  "description": "<p>Here is to inform you that the following {{ doctype }}({{ name }}) requires your attention/action.\n        <br>\n        The details of the request are as follows:\n        <br>\n        </p><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"1\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\">\n            <thead>\n                <tr>\n                    <th style=\"padding: 10px; text-align: left; background-color: #f2f2f2;\">Label</th>\n                    <th style=\"padding: 10px; text-align: left; background-color: #f2f2f2;\">Value</th>\n                </tr>\n            </thead>\n        <tbody>\n        \n            <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">Applicant Type</td>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">{{applicant_type}}</td>\n            </tr>\n            \n            <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">Applicant</td>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">{{applicant}}</td>\n            </tr>\n            \n            <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">Company</td>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">{{company}}</td>\n            </tr>\n            \n            <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">Posting Date</td>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">{{posting_date}}</td>\n            </tr>\n            \n            <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">Loan Product</td>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">{{loan_product}}</td>\n            </tr>\n            \n            <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">Rate of Interest (%) / Year</td>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">{{rate_of_interest}}</td>\n            </tr>\n            \n            <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">Mode of Payment</td>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">{{mode_of_payment}}</td>\n            </tr>\n            \n            <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">Disbursement Account</td>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">{{disbursement_account}}</td>\n            </tr>\n            \n            <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">Payment Account</td>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">{{payment_account}}</td>\n            </tr>\n            \n            <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">Loan Account</td>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">{{loan_account}}</td>\n            </tr>\n            \n            <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">Interest Income Account</td>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">{{interest_income_account}}</td>\n            </tr>\n            \n            <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">Penalty Income Account</td>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px;\">{{penalty_income_account}}</td>\n            </tr>\n            </tbody></table><p></p>",
